   760→        }
   761→      }
   762→    }
   763→  }
   764→}
   765→```
   766→
   767→### Transformation Pipeline
   768→
   769→```bash
   770→# Style Dictionary (converts tokens to various formats)
   771→npm install @tokens-studio/sd-cli
   772→
   773→# tokens.json → CSS variables → SCSS maps → TypeScript types → JSON
   774→sd build --config sd.config.json
