   802→
   803→## 8. Modern CSS Features for Production
   804→
   805→### :has() Pseudo-Class Patterns
   806→
   807→```css
   808→/* Form validation states */
   809→.input:has(input:invalid) {
   810→  border-color: var(--color-error-500);
   811→}
   812→
   813→.form-group:has(input:focus-visible) {
   814→  background: var(--color-surface-secondary);
   815→}
   816→
   817→/* Parent styling based on children */
   818→.flex-container:has(> :nth-child(n+4)) {
   819→  flex-direction: column; /* Switch to vertical if >3 items */
   820→}
   821→
   822→/* Responsive without queries */
   823→.product-grid:has(> :nth-child(n+9)) {
   824→  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
   825→}
   826→
   827→.product-grid:has(> :nth-child(n+5):nth-last-child(-n+4)) {
   828→  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
   829→}
   830→
   831→/* Adjacent sibling styling */
   832→.card:has(+ .card) {
   833→  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
   834→}
   835→```
   836→
   837→**Browser Support:** 97% in 2025 (all modern browsers)
   838→
   839→### @scope for Component Isolation
   840→
   841→```css
   842→/* Limit styles to specific scope without BEM naming */
   843→@scope (.modal-dialog) to (.modal-close) {
   844→  .heading { font-size: 1.5rem; }
   845→  .button { background: var(--color-primary-500); }
   846→  /* Styles don't leak out or in */
   847→}
   848→
