   852→  .content { font-size: var(--font-size-sm); }
   853→  .timestamp { color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
   854→
   855→  /* Child scope exclusion */
   856→  @scope (.nested-reply) to (.reply-end) {
   857→    .timestamp { font-size: 0.75rem; }
   858→  }
   859→}
   860→```
